entries.arrived_at_delivery: Stand by. Tracking Corellia Deep Mining Company supply vessel.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: Alright. Remember scare those Yavin boys real good. With enough pressure they will be forced to fold their operation. Keep up the good work.
entries.docking_started_delivery: So everything is on schedule. A few more attacks and then you will reveal yourselves as the return of the...Massassi. Thats funny. Those fools will run for it and we take over mining Yavin.
entries.found_loc_d: Corellia Deep Mining vessel located. Stand by for update of location.
entries.hello_d: Hey, they said you would be flying a strange ship but I didn't expect this. The Massassi plan is working great...keep it up and Yavin will be ours. Dock with me and I will drop off your payment.
entries.quest_dock2_d: The vessel was expecting mercenaries pretending to be the Massassi. They want to drop off payment for trying to chase the Yavin Mining Company out of the system.
entries.quest_location_d: Travel to the location supplied by the flight computer.
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Travel to the location supplied by the flight computer.
entries.split_quest_alert: Enemy fighters detected. They must be the ships that were supposed to pick up the payment that was mistakenly given to you. Destroy them before they can get word of this error out.
entries.title: Yavin System: Investigate the Competing Mining Co. Shuttle
entries.title_d: A vessel belonging to the Corellia Deep Mining Company has been spotted by your ship's computers. That company has no operations in the Yavin system. Find out what they are doing here.
